467
00:32:04,755 --> 00:32:06,623
    [PLAYING STOPS]             

468
00:32:08,091 --> 00:32:10,927
    [HARPSICHORD PLAYING]       

469
00:32:10,994 --> 00:32:12,862
        [PLAYING STOPS]         

470
00:32:18,636 --> 00:32:20,737
