492
00:34:46,233 --> 00:34:47,700
    YES, OF COURSE, MY DEAR.    

493
00:34:47,768 --> 00:34:49,335
    UNTIL THE MORNING,          
    AT ANY RATE.                

494
00:34:53,974 --> 00:34:55,407
