00:38:54,814 --> 00:38:58,184
             SHE SAID, "MARIA,  
             LEAVE THIS ROOM!"  

579
00:39:00,387 --> 00:39:02,688
                MY WIFE         
                SPOKE TO YOU?   

580
00:39:02,756 --> 00:39:03,722
                MY WIFE SPOKE-- 

581
00:39:03,790 --> 00:39:05,090
        NICHOLAS!               

582
00:39:19,072 --> 00:39:21,707
    NO ONE WILL EVER            
    ENTER THAT ROOM AGAIN.      

583
00:39:23,443 --> 00:39:24,377
