DOCTOR?                         

605
00:40:21,101 --> 00:40:22,668
    I AM NOT CERTAIN.           

606
00:40:22,736 --> 00:40:24,670
    BUT YOU DO YOU REMEMBER     

607
00:40:24,738 --> 00:40:27,540
