    ELIZABETH'S VOICE?          

608
00:40:27,608 --> 00:40:29,742
        WE HAVE ONLY            
    MARIA'S WORD FOR IT.        

609
00:40:29,809 --> 00:40:32,211
WE PROCEED ON                   
SIMILAR LINES, DOCTOR.          

610
00:40:32,279 --> 00:40:34,213
