    DON MEDINA!                 

622
00:41:12,002 --> 00:41:13,569
            [POUNDING]          

623
00:41:13,637 --> 00:41:14,803
                DON MEDINA!     

624
00:41:16,339 --> 00:41:18,574
THE KEY TO                      
ELIZABETH'S ROOM.               

625
00:41:18,642 --> 00:41:20,308
THE KEY, I SAID!                

626
00:41:25,481 --> 00:41:26,982
                    AGAIN?      

627
00:41:27,050 --> 00:41:28,684
[UNLOCKING DOOR]                

628
00:41:28,752 --> 00:41:30,586
                DO NOT GO THERE,
                NICHOLAS.       

629
