673
00:44:22,909 --> 00:44:25,711
            UNAWARE?            

674
00:44:25,779 --> 00:44:27,412
            TO PUNISH MYSELF?   

675
00:44:27,481 --> 00:44:29,949
NO, NICHOLAS, NO!               

676
00:44:30,016 --> 00:44:31,450
